data.name: ButtonTpl
data.value:
<Style xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml" TargetType="{x:Type Button}"> <Setter Property="Background" Value="[Btn.Color]"/> <Setter Property="BorderBrush" Value="[Btn.BorderColor]"/> <Setter Property="Foreground" Value="{DynamicResource {x:Static SystemColors.ControlTextBrushKey}}"/> <Setter Property="BorderThickness" Value="2"/> <Setter Property="HorizontalContentAlignment" Value="Center"/> <Setter Property="VerticalContentAlignment" Value="Center"/> <Setter Property="Padding" Value="1"/> <Setter Property="Template"> <Setter.Value> <ControlTemplate TargetType="{x:Type Button}">
<Border x:Name="innerborder" Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" BorderBrush="[Btn.BorderColor]" BorderThickness="1.5" SnapsToDevicePixels="true"> <Border x:Name="border" Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" Margin="1" BorderBrush="[Btn.Color]" BorderThickness="1" SnapsToDevicePixels="true"> <ContentPresenter x:Name="contentPresenter" Focusable="False" HorizontalAlignment="{TemplateBinding HorizontalContentAlignment}" Margin="{TemplateBinding Padding}" RecognizesAccessKey="True" SnapsToDevicePixels="{TemplateBinding SnapsToDevicePixels}" VerticalAlignment="{TemplateBinding VerticalContentAlignment}"/> </Border> </Border>
<ControlTemplate.Triggers> <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="true"> <Setter Property="Background" TargetName="border" Value="[Btn.BorderHoverColor]"/> <Setter Property="BorderBrush" TargetName="innerborder" Value="[Btn.BorderHoverColor]"/> </Trigger> <Trigger Property="IsPressed" Value="true"> <Setter Property="Background" TargetName="border" Value="[Btn.MouseDownColor]"/> <Setter Property="BorderBrush" TargetName="border" Value="[Btn.BorderMouseDownColor]"/> </Trigger> </ControlTemplate.Triggers> </ControlTemplate> </Setter.Value> </Setter> </Style>
